SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: Organization has clearly stated policy regarding conflict of interest policy and has communicated to all within the organization to employees .At each period end organization maintain the record of all transaction which employees has disclosed their interest and make sure that not to involve that person in the transaction that has conflict of interest and make sure that transaction is on arm's length basis without any significant influence by the person who has conflict within the transaction. IN case of non compliance with conflict of interest policy the person guilty has to face strict disciplinary action by the relevant dispute committee.
